c: 7
v: 187
t: "They ask you [Prophet] about the Last Hour, \"When will it come?\" Say, \"Knowledge about it rests only with my Lord; He alone will reveal when its time will come, it lies heavy on the heavens and the earth: it will suddenly overtake you.\" They will put questions to you as though you had full knowledge of it. Say, \"Knowledge about it rests only with God, though most people do not realize it"